::Prowl::

Prowl turns around and flies toward Iror Raptor. He slows down slightly as he 
sees that Iron Raptor isn't ready to catch him by the talons. He smiles as he 
gets an idea.

Prowl slows down and transforms into Robot Mode.

His wings propelling him forwards, he catches Iron Raptor by the waist, 
lifting her into the air. Resisting a terribly strong urge to kiss her, which 
would look pretty strange to the maximals back at the Ark, he flies toward 
the Ark.

Several dozen yards away from the Ark, Prowl sees Shocker fly in. He tightens 
his right arm around Iron Raptor, pressing her to him, takes his gun in his 
left hand, and fires at Shocker.
